  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Falajian Spice is a powdery brown spice harvested from =
the
  Falajian bush.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>It is highly valued for its distinctive rich flavor.
  Falajian spice is used extensively in exotic cuisine.<o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Falajian spice is made from the leaves of the Falajian =
bush
  by slowly drying them and then grinding them to a fine powder. Falajian
  bushes grow in swampy ponds on Marshy Swamp worlds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Occurrence: very rare<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Type: Luxury Resource</span><span lang=3DEN-GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
